        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Attractive",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", as “instruments of education for those who were children in age or character,” and offering in a striking form much for the memory to retain, and for the docile and truth-loving to learn; (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
